00196 const char *
00197 mnote_olympus_tag_get_name (MnoteOlympusTag t)
00198 {
00199         unsigned int i;
00200 
00201         for (i = 0; i < sizeof (table) / sizeof (table[0]); i++)

00209         unsigned int i;
00210

00217 const char *
00218 mnote_olympus_tag_get_description (MnoteOlympusTag t)
00219 {
00220         unsigned int i;
00221 
00222         for (i = 0; i < sizeof (table) / sizeof (table[0]); i++)

00224                         if (!table[i].description || !*table[i].description)
00225                                 return "";
